title: Crude suicide rate in Vietnam 2000 to 2015
summary: This statistic shows the forecast number of people in the united states who were using whatsapp as of the third quarter 2019 , sorted by age . Overall , high sales of u.s. adults aged between 18 and 29 years used the mobile app .
gold: This statistic shows the crude suicide rate in Vietnam from 2000 to 2015 . In 2015 , the crude suicide rate in Vietnam was approximately 7.4 deaths per 100,000 inhabitants .
